curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/10957' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8752-1Q", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8752-1Q is a single, high speed comparator,  which features a fast 6.5ns propagation delay. The  device is optimized for low voltage operation from 2.7V  to 5.5V. The SGM8752-1Q has a push-pull CMOS  output stage, which supports rail-to-rail output swing. It  can be compatible with CMOS and TTL logics.  The SGM8752-1Q features a small package. It is  suitable for portable and space-restricted applications.  The SGM8752-1Q is available in a Green SOT-23-5  package. It is operated over the -40℃ to +125℃  temperature range.  This device is AEC-Q100 qualified (Automotive  Electronics Council (AEC) standard Q100 Grade 1) and  it is suitable for automotive applications.        "}'
